画の参考にしてください。\nhttps://kwic.kwansei.ac.jp/cabinet/reference?typeCd=0&amp;cabinetId=557&amp;directLink=1\n※kwicへのリンクとなります（在学生のみ閲覧可）"], "学位授与の方針との関連Relationship to Diploma Policy1": ["Teacher corrections and feedback provided on every weekly assignment (dialogues)"], "成績評価Grading0": ["種別　Type備考　Note", "割合　Percentage", "評価基準等　Grading Criteria etc."], "成績評価Grading1": ["その他／Others (99)", "100 %", "Unit grammar quizzes 50% ; Final group project 20% ; Class participation/ weekly classwork (original dialogues ) 20% / vocabulary quizzes 10%"], "成績評価Grading2": ["備考　Note Although the final group project is only 20% of the final grade, completion of the project is required to pass the class."], "更新日時/Date of Update0": ["2026年04月02日 14時49分13秒"], "項番No.0": [], "項番No.1": ["2026年度", "春学期／Spring", "金曜３時限／Friday 3", "春学期／Spring", "５２１教室"]}, "campas": 4, "name": "【210】英語ＢIII　１／English BIII", "管理部署": 9, "単位数": 1, "担当者": "ガラス　ジョン　ビル（GARRAS JOHN BILL） ", "履修基準年度": "２年", "履修登録方法": "予備登録", "開講期": 1, "時限1": 30, "時限1_term": 0, "評価1": 6, "成績評価備考": "備考　Note\nAlthough the final group project is only 20% of the final grade, completion of the project is required to pass the class."}